@section Tokenising @axml{} documents


@cindex @library{nausicaa xml tags lexer}, library
@cindex Library @library{nausicaa xml tags lexer}


The library @library{nausicaa tags lexer} implements a lexer compliant
with the @axml{} recommendation version 1.0.  The lexer is built on top
of the @library{nausicaa silex} parser generator (@pxref{silex}).

@menu
* tags lexer full::             Full lexer table.
* tags lexer params::           Full lexer--tabl semantic--action
                                parameters.
* tags lexer makers::           Full lexer token makers.
* tags lexer strings::          Reading strings.
* tags lexer custom::           Customising the lexer.
@end menu

