@section Parsing a stream of @axml{} tokens


@cindex @library{nausicaa xml tags parser}, library
@cindex Library @library{nausicaa xml tags parser}


The library @library{nausicaa xml tags parser} implements a lexer
compliant with the @axml{} recommendation version 1.0.  The lexer is
built on top of the @library{nausicaa lalr} parser generator
(@pxref{lalr}) and it is meant to be used with the lexer @api{} exported
by the @library{nausicaa xml tags lexer} library (@pxref{tags lexer}).

@menu
* tags parser parsing::         Parsing source code.
* tags parser params::          Parser semantic actions parameters.
* tags parser makers::          Parser datum makers.
* tags parser custom::          Customising the parser.
@end menu

