@section A collection of common strings


@cindex @library{nausicaa xml tags fixed-strings}, library
@cindex Library @library{nausicaa xml tags fixed-strings}


The library @library{nausicaa xml tags fixed-strings} exports bindings
to common strings which are meant to be comparable using @func{eq?}.

@c ------------------------------------------------------------

@subsubheading @axml{} tag strings


@defvr Constant tag-open
Bound to the string @samp{"<"}.
@end defvr


@defvr Constant tag-close
Bound to the string @samp{">"}.
@end defvr


@defvr Constant processor-instructions-open
Bound to the string @samp{"<?"}.
@end defvr


@defvr Constant processor-instructions-close
Bound to the string @samp{"?>"}.
@end defvr


@defvr Constant comment-open
Bound to the string @samp{"<!--"}.
@end defvr


@defvr Constant comment-close
Bound to the string @samp{"-->"}.
@end defvr



